metadata.name: DIY CRYPTO PUNK No. 1
metadata.description:
I wanted to capture the mental chaos that comes with processing the reality we're living. Encapsulating the struggle in the divisions we face and the constant meta-growth that ultimately is an overwhelming feeling of 'fuck the system or be one with.'

Photo of musician American Teeth (1 of 4)

DIY Set made out of the mid-90s / 2000s old computer and television parts placed on cardboard.
